      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a surgical throttle response and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. This chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcements and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the mechanical vitals are robust. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, offering the balanced handling and communicative steering feedback this platform is renowned for. A well-maintained driver\u2019s car that balances raw performance with mechanical longevity.",
